data.description: Nestled on Whitehaven Road, this delightful abode boasts a welcoming ambiance and modern comforts. Step inside to discover three generously sized bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, providing ample space for relaxation and privacy. The convenience of an upstairs laundry makes chores a breeze, while the versatile loft area offers endless possibilities, whether it's a cozy reading nook or a home office. Recent upgrades, including a new roof and water heater, ensure peace of mind and added value. Outside, the backyard beckons with picturesque pond views, creating an idyllic setting for outdoor gatherings or peaceful moments of reflection. Whether you're enjoying the tranquil scenery or the comfortable interior, this home offers the perfect blend of functionality and charm for everyday living.
